title: VA-World Of House Vol.5 (Double CD Mixed by Jim Kashel)

VA-WORLD OF HOUSE 5 (DOUBLE CD MIXED BY JIM KASHEL)
Release Date: 01/08/2013
Release Label: Prokfillah Studios (White Label)
Quality (kbps): 320kbps
Total Tracks: 32 tracks
Genere: Progressive House, Electro House, Trap, Dubstep, Drum & Bass and Neurofunk
